properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 5 at 2:15PM MST until February 7 at 4:00PM MST by NWS Salt Lake City UT
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts around 60 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Southwest Wyoming.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Thursday to 4 PM MST Friday.

* IMPACTS...High winds may cause light unsecured objects to become
airborne. Blowing snow may cause local visibility restrictions
and slick roads. Travel could be difficult especially for high
profile vehicles and those towing trailers. Wind sensitive
operations will be impacted.
properties.instruction:
People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown
around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM THURSDAY TO 4 PM MST FRIDAY
